  1446→+---
  1447→+
  1448→+## Scope Summary
  1449→+
  1450→+Migrate `TrendingCarousel.jsx` from the catalog repo into `packages/extensions/reco/TrendingProductsWidget/` using the ADR-20 extensions structure. The widget is broken into internal atoms/molecules (not publicly exported) and one assembled widget component + one dumb hook (publicly exported).
  1451→+
  1452→+---
  1453→+
  1454→+## What Does NOT Move
  1455→+
  1456→+| Catalog piece | Why | How replaced |
  1457→+|---|---|---|
  1458→+| `FavoritesProvider` / `useFavorites` | Auth-aware, catalog-specific context | Catalog wraps widget with `FavoritesProvider`; injects button via `renderFavoriteButton` render prop |
  1459→+| `ProductCardPriceDetails` | Deeply catalog-specific: Rollbar, AB tests, `useProductCardPriceDetails` data fetching | `RecommendationsProductCard` exposes `renderPriceDetails` render prop |
  1460→+| `useTrendingProductsWrapper` / `usePromotionalProducts` | React Query, catalog API config | Replaced by dumb `useTrendingProducts` hook that accepts a `fetcher` function |
  1461→+| `firePromoTrendingRecommendationClickEvent` / `ViewEvent` | Catalog analytics utils | Replaced by `onWidgetViewed` / `onCardViewed` / `onCardClicked` callback props on the widget |
  1462→+| `useBreakpoint` (catalog hook) | Catalog-specific | Re-implement as local `useMediaQuery`-based hook inside widget |
  1463→+| MUI `styled()` | v0 pattern, no MUI in new code | CSS Modules |
  1464→+
