  1712→+
  1713→+## TrendingProductsWidget Assembly
  1714→+
  1715→+**Responsive slidesPerView logic** (preserve from `TrendingCarousel.jsx`):
  1716→+
  1717→+| Breakpoint | Products count | slidesPerView | spacing |
  1718→+|---|---|---|---|
  1719→+| Mobile (`≤ 768px`) | ≥ 3 | 1.6 | 8px |
  1720→+| Mobile | < 3 | `'auto'` | 8px |
  1721→+| Desktop | ≥ 5 | 4 | 16px |
  1722→+| Desktop | < 5 | `'auto'` | 16px |
  1723→+
  1724→+**Arrow visibility:** `showArrows = slidesPerView !== 'auto' && !isMobile`
  1725→+
  1726→+**Widget behavior:**
  1727→+- `isLoading` → render `LoadingSkeleton`
  1728→+- `products.length === 0` → return `null`
  1729→+- Viewport visibility: `IntersectionObserver` on wrapper → `onWidgetViewed(products)` fires once
  1730→+- Card click → `onCardClicked(product, index)`
  1731→+- Card in viewport → `onCardViewed(product, index)` (per-card IntersectionObserver, optional phase 2)
  1732→+
  1733→+**`FavoritesProvider` is NOT wrapped here** — catalog is responsible for wrapping:
  1734→+```tsx
  1735→+// catalog (after migration)
  1736→+<FavoritesProvider pageType={PageType.SUBCATEGORY}>
  1737→+  <TrendingProductsWidget
  1738→+    products={products}
  1739→+    isLoading={isLoading}
  1740→+    renderFavoriteButton={(product) => (
  1741→+      <FavoriteButton
  1742→+        styleId={product.styleId}
  1743→+        isFavorited={isFavorited(product.styleId)}
  1744→+        onToggle={...}
  1745→+      />
  1746→+    )}
  1747→+    renderPriceDetails={(product) => (
  1748→+      <ProductCardPriceDetails
  1749→+        defaultUnitPrices={product.defaultUnitPrices}
  1750→+        productId={product.styleId}
  1751→+        quantity={product.defaultQuoteQty}
  1752→+        {...catalogSpecificProps}
  1753→+      />
  1754→+    )}
  1755→+  />
  1756→+</FavoritesProvider>
  1757→+```
